#: backend/templates/core/landing.html:66
msgid ""
"Every recommendation exposes its sources, formula, and uncertainty. No black "
"boxes."
msgstr ""
"Jede Empfehlung legt ihre Quellen, Formel und Unsicherheit offen. Keine "
"Black Boxes."

#: backend/templates/core/landing.html:70
msgid "Self-hostable"
